    "Using the generated counterfactual dataset, we train a multi-step action value model MPA (Ours) VAD Collision Collision Braking Yielding Nominal ScenesReconstructed Reconstructed Ground Truth Ground TruthQ(o t, s t, a t; T) = T t=1 γ t r(s, a t)based on four interpretable principles: route following Q route, lane distance Q dist, collision avoidance Q collision, and speed compliance Q speed.",
